query:
CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS `facility_locations` (
  `id` INT AUTO_INCREMENT PRIMARY KEY,
  `carrier` VARCHAR(100) NOT NULL,
  `facilityName` VARCHAR(500) NOT NULL,
  `facilityType` VARCHAR(100),
  `address` TEXT,
  `city` VARCHAR(255),
  `state` VARCHAR(100),
  `zip` VARCHAR(20),
  `country` VARCHAR(100),
  `latitude` DECIMAL(10, 7),
  `longitude` DECIMAL(10, 7),
  `geocodedAt` TIMESTAMP NULL,
  `confidenceLabel` VARCHAR(50) NOT NULL,
  `verificationSources` JSON,
  `verificationNotes` TEXT,
  `lastVerified` TIMESTAMP NULL,
  `verifiedBy` INT,
  `isAnomaly` BOOLEAN DEFAULT FALSE,
  `anomalyReason` TEXT,
  `averageProcessingMinutes` INT,
  `totalScans` INT DEFAULT 0,
  `delayIncidents` INT DEFAULT 0,
  `performanceScore` DECIMAL(5,2),
  `createdAt` TIMESTAMP DEFAULT CURRENT_TIMESTAMP NOT NULL,
  `updatedAt` TIMESTAMP DEFAULT CURRENT_TIMESTAMP ON UPDATE CURRENT_TIMESTAMP NOT NULL,
  INDEX `carrier_idx` (`carrier`),
  INDEX `confidence_idx` (`confidenceLabel`),
  INDEX `location_idx` (`latitude`, `longitude`),
  INDEX `performance_idx` (`performanceScore`),
  UNIQUE INDEX `unique_facility` (`carrier`, `facilityName`(255), `city`, `state`)
)
